The Single Line Patterns are sized to fit a 12x12 inch mat and are divided in 9 repeatable pattern blocks.  If you foil a little larger than your project and then cut out the card or shape you have full coverage.
Ungroup once for smaller projects and simply delete redundant blocks so you don't waste your foil :)
Ungroup a second time to move individual geometric elements and have fun creating custom adjustments or altering the pattern
The blocks can be duplicated to seamlessly repeat the pattern. So you can even make a smaller, more intricate pattern while still being able to cover a larger area :)
